reviewText: Ive finally found the perfect dvd that equals that of an actually belly dance class!!!
Shahrzad is so talented and graceful, and she shared some great techniques love it!
Shahrad is a wonderful belly dancer and teacher.
Shahrzad is such a relaxed and controlled instructor and performer in this DVD.  She makes the moves become effortless.  My thanks!
I absolutely loved the floor exercise to help the shimmies get strong and even.....IT WORKS!
